trailingComments.value:
*
   * inspect ExportDefaultDeclaration.
   *
   * case1: separated export
   *
   * ```javascript
   * class Foo {}
   * export default Foo;
   * ```
   *
   * case2: export instance(directly).
   *
   * ```javascript
   * class Foo {}
   * export default new Foo();
   * ```
   *
   * case3: export instance(indirectly).
   *
   * ```javascript
   * class Foo {}
   * let foo = new Foo();
   * export default foo;
   * ```
   *
   * @private
   * @todo support function export.
